file.name: another-client-api-v1.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.7.9
  title: Another
  license:
    name: MIT
paths:
  '/client-api/v1/other-ones':
    get:
      summary: List all other ones
      operationId: listOtherOnes
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A paged array of other ones
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/OtherOnes"
components:
  schemas:
    OtherOnes:
      type: object
      properties:
        -id:
          type: string
          description: The id of this one.
        -oneId:
          type: string
          description: The id of the original One
